# VisionCraft core

This repo streams Minecraft stereo to Apple Vision Pro via a Mac host and/or a native visionOS companion.

Before any Apple-platform change:

1. Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) and identify **mac-host** vs **visionos-app**.
2. Read the golden files listed there for the path you are editing.
3. Cross-check [bridge/protocol.md](../../bridge/protocol.md) when touching pose, hand, frames, or view config.

Do not guess Compositor Services, ARKit, or VideoToolbox APIs. Use Context7 (`/websites/developer_apple`) or official documentation URLs.

Platform targets: macOS 26+, visionOS 26+, Xcode 26+.
